                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Dazerien lost a few toes to frostbite, but what clings in his mind is the agony of the cold that seeped into his bones as he endured a particularly cruel punishment from his father. The first time each round he takes cold damage, Dazerien takes @Damage[2d6[mental]] damage and becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 1} (@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 2} if the triggering cold damage was in excess of 20).</p>"
